{"tid":1657254,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"留言侮辱中大生 黑警跑手同贊助商終止合作","createTime":"2019-10-16T04:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T08:19:53.000Z","uid":73057,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"13df07940395b65e14a756365c1ce45468f4c62b","tid":1657254,"uid":73057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:06:39.000Z","msg":"早前有疑似警員在網上發表侮辱大學生言論，同為業餘跑手的他被披露受到運動品牌Asics贊助。有網民到Asics社交網站專頁留言，冀該品牌正視事件。Asics今日公佈，與疑為該名警員的易嘉麟已終止贊助協議。<br />\n<br />\n日前在網上流傳一張社交網站截圖，消息指一位外號為「忌廉」的跑手指「啲中大生真係好吹得。個直播令人想笑。拘捕後被性暴？唔去驗傷？痴」疑為警員易嘉麟的帳號則留言「做天使做到shot（應該為short）左（咗）」，侮辱受害人。事後有網民指，易嘉麟為Asics贊助的跑手，有網民就到Asics社交平台專頁，要求該品牌交代。Asics今日指，易嘉麟已主動提出解除贊助協議，並已經生效。<br />\n<br />\n據長跑界消息人士指，易嘉麟乃香港警隊中特別任務連成員，並沒有在前線參與處理示威的職務，但多次在網上發表侮辱示威者言論，引起多人不滿。據悉Asics一直考慮解決事件的方法，最後易嘉麟主動提出終止合作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20191015/XYFDZ432QF5ZJBGVGKOMAM6WYE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20191015%2FXYFDZ432QF5ZJBGVGKOMAM6WYE%2F&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVibpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=8ca25be8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20191015%2FXYFDZ432QF5ZJBGVGKOMAM6WYE%2F&h=6b5dde36\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20191015/XYFDZ432QF5ZJBGVGKOMAM6WYE/</a><br />\n<br />\n請和理非繼續運用投訴同精明消費力量<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce831d7cfc4ca62d87cbf4bb29e7ace496657589","tid":1657254,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:06:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/afoWPNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FafoWPNY.jpg&h=041452ea&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b3299ae5e95353b72e0853f28637b511ca84c72d","tid":1657254,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:07:58.000Z","msg":"Project reference"},{"pid":"546ff6eeb1770ce6fc0